---
// src/components/Sidebar.astro
---

<aside class="w-full lg:w-[320px] flex-shrink-0">
    <div class="h-full space-y-8">
        
        {/* 1. 運営者プロフィール */}
        <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-green-600 pb-2 mb-4 text-base">この記事を書いた人</h3>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
                <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/shigagolf-e31e6.firebasestorage.app/practice_ranges/image_archive/gallery/author.png" alt="関（せき）" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover border border-slate-200">
                <div>
                    <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 m-0 text-base">関（せき）</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-green-700 font-bold m-0 mt-1">初心者向けゴルフ施設レビュアー</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                ゴルフ歴1年未満。初心者の壁をなくすため、滋賀県の練習場を自腹で巡り「忖度なしのリアルな情報」を発信中！
            </p>
            <div class="text-right">
                <a href="/about/" class="text-xs text-green-700 font-bold hover:underline">詳しいプロフィールを見る ＞</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-8">

        {/* 2. 大まとめ（ハブ）記事バナー */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <a href="/articles/hikone-hub/" class="block">
                <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/shigagolf-e31e6.firebasestorage.app/practice_ranges/image_archive/gallery/hikone-matome.jpg" alt="彦根・多賀ゴルフ練習場完全ガイド" class="w-full h-auto">
            </a>
        </div>

        {/* 3. 初心者応援！ゴルフデビューロードマップ */}
        <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-green-600 pb-2 mb-4 text-base">ゴルフデビュー必読ガイド</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm">
                {/* ステップ1：打ちっぱなし */}
                <li>
                    <a href="/articles/beginner-complete-guide/" class="group flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">1</span>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 block">練習場デビューに</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-700 group-hover:text-green-700 group-hover:underline font-semibold leading-tight block">「空振りしても恥ずかしくない」初めての打ちっぱなし完全ガイド</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                {/* ステップ2：ショートコース */}
                <li>
                    <a href="/articles/shiga-short-courses/" class="group flex gap-3 items-start"> {/* ※実際のURLに合わせてください */}
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">2</span>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 block">🔥 圧倒的人気記事</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-700 group-hover:text-green-700 group-hover:underline font-semibold leading-tight block">滋賀のショートコースは2ヶ所だけ！【安曇川 vs 365長浜】徹底比較</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                {/* ステップ3：3つのバッグ */}
                <li>
                    <a href="/articles/beginner-guide/" class="group flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">3</span>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 block">本番の服装・マナーに</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-700 group-hover:text-green-700 group-hover:underline font-semibold leading-tight block">【失敗談あり】初コースで焦らない「3つのバッグ」仕分け術</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                {/* ステップ4：楽天GORA */}
                <li>
                    <a href="/articles/rakuten-gora-point-guide/" class="group flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">4</span>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 block">お得にコースを予約する</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-700 group-hover:text-green-700 group-hover:underline font-semibold leading-tight block">【楽天GORA】初回予約で損しない！最大19,000pt獲得ワザ</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</aside>